001package com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.response.historyLog;
002
003import com.google.common.base.Preconditions;
004import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.annotations.HistoryLogProps;
005import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.helpers.Bytes;
006
007@HistoryLogProps(
008    opCode = 3,
009    displayName = "Basal Rate Change",
010    usedByTidepool = true
011)
012public class BasalRateChangeHistoryLog extends HistoryLog {
013    
014    private float commandBasalRate;
015    private float baseBasalRate;
016    private float maxBasalRate;
017    private int insulinDeliveryProfile;
018    private int changeTypeId;
019    
020    public BasalRateChangeHistoryLog() {}
021    public BasalRateChangeHistoryLog(long pumpTimeSec, long sequenceNum, float commandBasalRate, float baseBasalRate, float maxBasalRate, int insulinDeliveryProfile, int changeTypeId) {
022        super(pumpTimeSec, sequenceNum);
023        this.cargo = buildCargo(pumpTimeSec, sequenceNum, commandBasalRate, baseBasalRate, maxBasalRate, insulinDeliveryProfile, changeTypeId);
024        this.commandBasalRate = commandBasalRate;
025        this.baseBasalRate = baseBasalRate;
026        this.maxBasalRate = maxBasalRate;
027        this.insulinDeliveryProfile = insulinDeliveryProfile;
028        this.changeTypeId = changeTypeId;
029        
030    }
031
032    public BasalRateChangeHistoryLog(float commandBasalRate, float baseBasalRate, float maxBasalRate, int insulinDeliveryProfile, int changeTypeId) {
033        this(0, 0, commandBasalRate, baseBasalRate, maxBasalRate, insulinDeliveryProfile, changeTypeId);
034    }
035
036    public int typeId() {
037        return 3;
038    }
039
040    /**
041     * <table border="1">
042     * <caption>Parsed fields for BasalRateChangeHistoryLog:</caption>
043     * <tr><td><code>commandBasalRate</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readFloat(raw, 10)</code></td></tr>
044     * <tr><td><code>baseBasalRate</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readFloat(raw, 14)</code></td></tr>
045     * <tr><td><code>maxBasalRate</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readFloat(raw, 18)</code></td></tr>
046     * <tr><td><code>insulinDeliveryProfile</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readShort(raw, 22)</code></td></tr>
047     * <tr><td><code>changeTypeId</code></td><td><code>raw[24]</code></td></tr>
048     * </table>
049     */
050    public void parse(byte[] raw) {
051        Preconditions.checkArgument(raw.length == 26);
052        this.cargo = raw;
053        parseBase(raw);
054        this.commandBasalRate = Bytes.readFloat(raw, 10);
055        this.baseBasalRate = Bytes.readFloat(raw, 14);
056        this.maxBasalRate = Bytes.readFloat(raw, 18);
057        this.insulinDeliveryProfile = Bytes.readShort(raw, 22);
058        this.changeTypeId = raw[24];
059        
060    }
061
062    /**
063     * <table border="1">
064     * <caption>Byte layout for BasalRateChangeHistoryLog.buildCargo(...):</caption>
065     * <tr><th>Offset</th><th>Description</th></tr>
066     * <tr><td>0</td><td><code>new byte[]{3} [element 0]</code></td></tr>
067     * <tr><td>1</td><td><code>new byte[]{0} [element 1]</code></td></tr>
068     * <tr><td>2</td><td><code>toUint32(pumpTimeSec) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
069     * <tr><td>3</td><td><code>toUint32(pumpTimeSec) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
070     * <tr><td>4</td><td><code>toUint32(pumpTimeSec) [byte 2]</code></td></tr>
071     * <tr><td>5</td><td><code>toUint32(pumpTimeSec) [byte 3]</code></td></tr>
072     * <tr><td>6</td><td><code>toUint32(sequenceNum) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
073     * <tr><td>7</td><td><code>toUint32(sequenceNum) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
074     * <tr><td>8</td><td><code>toUint32(sequenceNum) [byte 2]</code></td></tr>
075     * <tr><td>9</td><td><code>toUint32(sequenceNum) [byte 3]</code></td></tr>
076     * <tr><td>10</td><td><code>toFloat(commandBasalRate) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
077     * <tr><td>11</td><td><code>toFloat(commandBasalRate) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
078     * <tr><td>12</td><td><code>toFloat(commandBasalRate) [byte 2]</code></td></tr>
079     * <tr><td>13</td><td><code>toFloat(commandBasalRate) [byte 3]</code></td></tr>
080     * <tr><td>14</td><td><code>toFloat(baseBasalRate) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
081     * <tr><td>15</td><td><code>toFloat(baseBasalRate) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
082     * <tr><td>16</td><td><code>toFloat(baseBasalRate) [byte 2]</code></td></tr>
083     * <tr><td>17</td><td><code>toFloat(baseBasalRate) [byte 3]</code></td></tr>
084     * <tr><td>18</td><td><code>toFloat(maxBasalRate) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
085     * <tr><td>19</td><td><code>toFloat(maxBasalRate) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
086     * <tr><td>20</td><td><code>toFloat(maxBasalRate) [byte 2]</code></td></tr>
087     * <tr><td>21</td><td><code>toFloat(maxBasalRate) [byte 3]</code></td></tr>
088     * <tr><td>22</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(insulinDeliveryProfile) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
089     * <tr><td>23</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(insulinDeliveryProfile) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
090     * <tr><td>24</td><td><code>new byte[]{(byte) changeType} [element 0]</code></td></tr>
091     * <tr><td>25</td><td><code>new byte[]{0} [element 1]</code></td></tr>
092     * </table>
093     */
094    public static byte[] buildCargo(long pumpTimeSec, long sequenceNum, float commandBasalRate, float baseBasalRate, float maxBasalRate, int insulinDeliveryProfile, int changeType) {
095        return Bytes.combine(
096            new byte[]{3, 0},
097            Bytes.toUint32(pumpTimeSec),
098            Bytes.toUint32(sequenceNum),
099            Bytes.toFloat(commandBasalRate), 
100            Bytes.toFloat(baseBasalRate), 
101            Bytes.toFloat(maxBasalRate), 
102            Bytes.firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(insulinDeliveryProfile), 
103            new byte[]{ (byte) changeType, 0 });
104    }
105
106    /**
107     * @return the basal rate which is being changed to
108     */
109    public float getCommandBasalRate() {
110        return commandBasalRate;
111    }
112
113    /**
114     * @return the basal rate which is default for the current profile segment
115     */
116    public float getBaseBasalRate() {
117        return baseBasalRate;
118    }
119
120    /**
121     * @return the maximum allowed basal rate in the profile settings
122     */
123    public float getMaxBasalRate() {
124        return maxBasalRate;
125    }
126
127    /**
128     * @return the ID of the Insulin Delivery Profile (IDP)
129     */
130    public int getInsulinDeliveryProfile() {
131        return insulinDeliveryProfile;
132    }
133
134    public int getChangeTypeId() {
135        return changeTypeId;
136    }
137
138    enum ChangeType {
139        TIMED_SEGMENT(1),
140        NEW_PROFILE(2),
141        TEMP_RATE_START(4),
142        TEMP_RATE_END(8),
143        PUMP_SUSPENDED(16),
144        PUMP_RESUMED(32),
145        PUMP_SHUT_DOWN(64),
146        ;
147
148        final int id;
149        ChangeType(int id) {
150            this.id = id;
151        }
152
153        public static ChangeType fromId(int id) {
154            for (ChangeType c : values()) {
155                if (c.id == id) {
156                    return c;
157                }
158            }
159            return null;
160        }
161    }
162
163    /**
164     * @return the reason that the basal rate was changed
165     */
166    public ChangeType getChangeType() {
167        return ChangeType.fromId(changeTypeId);
168    }
169    
170}
